messages.messageBody:
Just
6 days left to receive all the awesome Earlybird Registration Bonuses for the 4th Annual Unschoolers Waterpark
Gathering!

All those who register by Feb.15, will receive $45 in Kalahari Gift Cards, PLUS free Mini Golf Passes! -
(they have an awesome new Black Light Mini Golf Course, where the balls
and course glow with a rainbow of colors!) (FYI- regular rates for mini
golf are $6/person)





Don't hesitate and miss-out on these great Earlybird Deadline Bonuses.
For further details, latest updates and to begin connecting with others,  join our yahoo group at:

http://groups.yahoo.com/group/UWG/




~ Carol Reinhard - UWG Coordinator
